#: src/types/city-info.ts
msgid "Current amount of gold in the treasury.\n"
"Affects the city's ability to maintain and expand its infrastructure.\n"
"Buildings, units, and other expenses are paid from the treasury."
msgstr "Current amount of gold in the treasury.\n"
"Affects the city's ability to maintain and expand its infrastructure.\n"
"Buildings, units, and other expenses are paid from the treasury."

#: src/types/city-info.ts
msgid "Current animosity direction of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's efficiency in its crackdown and military actions.\n"
"The direction indicates which faction or city the animosity is primarily directed towards."
msgstr "Current animosity direction of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's efficiency in its crackdown and military actions.\n"
"The direction indicates which faction or city the animosity is primarily directed towards."

#: src/types/city-info.ts
msgid "Current animosity influence of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's ability to manage conflicts and rivalries.\n"
"High animosity influence can lead to increased tension and decreased stability."
msgstr "Current animosity influence of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's ability to manage conflicts and rivalries.\n"
"High animosity influence can lead to increased tension and decreased stability."

#: src/types/city-info.ts
msgid "Current crime influence of the city.\n"
"Affected by the city's stability.\n"
"High crime influence can lead to increased unrest and decreased stability."
msgstr "Current crime influence of the city.\n"
"Affected by the city's stability.\n"
"High crime influence can lead to increased unrest and decreased stability."

#: src/components/GameContentContainer.tsx
#~ msgid "Current culture influence of the city"
#~ msgstr "Current culture influence of the city"

#: src/types/city-info.ts
msgid "Current culture influence of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's ability to shape societal values and norms.\n"
"High culture influence can lead to increased unity and citizen engagement."
msgstr "Current culture influence of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's ability to shape societal values and norms.\n"
"High culture influence can lead to increased unity and citizen engagement."

