#~ msgstr "Current productivity of the city"

#: src/types/city-info.ts
msgid "Current productivity of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's ability to produce goods and services.\n"
"Consumed by production activities, units, and other expenses."
msgstr "Current productivity of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's ability to produce goods and services.\n"
"Consumed by production activities, units, and other expenses."

#: src/components/GameContentContainer.tsx
#~ msgid "Current religion influence of the city"
#~ msgstr "Current religion influence of the city"

#: src/types/city-info.ts
msgid "Current religion influence of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's ability to shape and spread religious practices and beliefs.\n"
"High religion influence can lead to increased stability and effectiveness in spreading religion to nearby cities."
msgstr "Current religion influence of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's ability to shape and spread religious practices and beliefs.\n"
"High religion influence can lead to increased stability and effectiveness in spreading religion to nearby cities."

