#~ msgid "Current stability level of the city"
#~ msgstr "Current stability level of the city"

#: src/types/city-info.ts
msgid "Current stability level of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's overall performance and citizen satisfaction.\n"
"Low stability can lead to unrest, riots, and decreased productivity.\n"
"High stability can lead to increased growth and prosperity."
msgstr "Current stability level of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's overall performance and citizen satisfaction.\n"
"Low stability can lead to unrest, riots, and decreased productivity.\n"
"High stability can lead to increased growth and prosperity."

#: src/components/GameContentContainer.tsx
#~ msgid "Current technology strength of the city"
#~ msgstr "Current technology strength of the city"

#: src/types/city-info.ts
msgid "Current technology strength of the city.\n"
"Affects the whole empire's ability to innovate and advance.\n"
"High technology strength can lead to increased efficiency in research and productivity generation."
msgstr "Current technology strength of the city.\n"
"Affects the whole empire's ability to innovate and advance.\n"
"High technology strength can lead to increased efficiency in research and productivity generation."

#: src/components/GameContentContainer.tsx
#~ msgid "Current trade influence of the city"
#~ msgstr "Current trade influence of the city"

#: src/types/city-info.ts
msgid "Current trade influence of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's ability to create fortune, generate wealth, and engage in commerce.\n"
"High trade influence can lead to increased income and economic growth."
msgstr "Current trade influence of the city.\n"
"Affects the city's ability to create fortune, generate wealth, and engage in commerce.\n"
"High trade influence can lead to increased income and economic growth."

