#: src/types/city-info.ts
msgid "Current war weariness influence of the city.\n"
"Affected by the city's military engagements and overall stability.\n"
"High war weariness influence can lead to decreased military effectiveness and increased unrest."
msgstr "Current war weariness influence of the city.\n"
"Affected by the city's military engagements and overall stability.\n"
"High war weariness influence can lead to decreased military effectiveness and increased unrest."

